org.archive.wayback.replay.html.transformer

Class RegexReplaceStringTransformer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.archive.wayback.replay.html.rewrite.RewriteRule
      • org.archive.wayback.replay.html.transformer.RegexReplaceStringTransformer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StringTransformer, org.springframework.beans.factory.BeanNameAware

    public class RegexReplaceStringTransformer
extends RewriteRule
implements StringTransformer
    Replaces all occurrence of regular expression regex in input with replacement. If the context has disable-rewrite- beanName policy, transformation is disabled.
